{
  "id": "641fbd5c7102aa001babd56a",
  "title": "物に尊敬を感じられる才能",
  "created": 1679801693,
  "updated": 1679801794,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "641fbd91aff09e0000ca1da0",
      "text": "物に尊敬を感じられる才能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801745,
      "updated": 1679801752
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d77",
      "text": ">[shanegJP https://twitter.com/shanegJP/status/1639820629062070272] ChatGPT・GPT-4・ChatGPTプラグインの全てで使われてる「呪文」、そして2022年一番記憶に残った言語モデルの論文は @Matsuo_Lab 松尾研の小島君と岩沢さん  @yusuke_iwasawa_ さんが見つけました。私も論文を手伝いましたが素晴らしい発見でした。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801717
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d7c",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d7d",
      "text": "> なぜこれを日本人が見つけられたか？...（次）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d7e",
      "text": "> >jaguring1: ChatGPTを賢くする呪文",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d7f",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d80",
      "text": "> 「Let's think step by step（一歩ずつ考えよう）」の話が書かれている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d81",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d82",
      "text": "> この呪文の発見者でもある小島武さん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d83",
      "text": "> 「大規模言語モデルの中には直感的に答える思考法と、論理的な思考法の双方が獲得されているのではないか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d84",
      "text": "> https://nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUC22BVO0S3A320C2000000/…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d87",
      "text": ">[shanegJP https://twitter.com/shanegJP/status/1639820630597210112] 私の持論は「日本人が一番AIに感動する才能を持ってるから」だと思います。「物」に「人の（ような）感動や尊敬」を感じられる才能（[神道]、八百万の神から？）は、ChatGPT時代に最高です。楽しみにしています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801794
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d89",
      "text": ">[shanegJP https://twitter.com/shanegJP/status/1639822013496971265] 「物」(AI、GPT、ChatGPT）に「人のように」ただ聞いてみる。今じゃ当たり前ですが、アメリカ人や他にはなかった発想だと思います。これも：",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d8a",
      "text": "> >shanegJP: 10年前、日本のロボットラボを見学時、記憶に残った言葉：「日本はルンバを作れなかった。」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d8b",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d8c",
      "text": "> ただ、それは「ドラえもんを作りたかったから。」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d8d",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d8e",
      "text": "> 深層学習も同じだと思う。ImageNet、BERTも、所詮は機械学習。日本は40年前から汎用性人工知能しか見てない。故にChatGPTが強く刺さったと思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d91",
      "text": ">[shanegJP https://twitter.com/shanegJP/status/1639828671354802178] 当たり前ですがGPT-4の論文でも引用され使われてます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d92",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679801693,
      "updated": 1679801693
    },
    {
      "id": "641fbd5daff09e0000ca1d93",
      "text": "> GPT-4論文： https://cdn.openai.com/papers/gpt-4.pdf… 小島君の論文：https://arxiv.org/abs/2205.11916",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
